sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant AuthService
    participant API
    participant DB
    Client->>AuthService: login(user, pass)
    activate AuthService
    AuthService->>DB: lookup(user)
    DB-->>AuthService: user record
    alt valid credentials
        AuthService-->>Client: JWT token
    else invalid
        AuthService-->>Client: 401 Unauthorized
    end
    deactivate AuthService
    Client->>API: GET /data
    Note over API: validates JWT
    API->>DB: query(user_id)
    DB-->>API: results
    API-->>Client: 200 OK
